== Features ==
* music library
* random playback
* repeat "playlist", "track" or "track once" options
* pause on phone calls
* prevent suspend
* volume controll

== Known Bugs ==
* Somtimes playback stops, but GUI is still responsive, until play button is hit.
** Seems to be a problem with gstreamer. Maybe it locks up.
* PyRok crashes on loading a new OGG file sometimes. It seems that gstreamer make pygame crash
* Sometimes (seldom) the Freerunner freeze compleatly
** Reason unknown

